Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.project

Class ProjectProfileDto

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.project.ProjectProfileDto
public class ProjectProfileDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object for the profile of a project. This class encapsulates detailed information about a project, including its name, system name, member type, status, and creation date.
